name: I Wonder Who They Found (V)
Lore: '''General Solo, is your strike team assembled?''',
Text: 'Use 2 Force to deploy on Han or Back Door; draw top card of Used Pile. Non-Jedi, non-[Permanent Weapon] Rebels are defense value +2 and immune to attrition < 3. May place this Effect out of play to cancel the targeting of a weapon at same or related site.',
